response.overview: AEW presents Double or Nothing - Live on from the Desert Diamond Arena in Glendale, AZ. The 2025 Owen Hart Foundation Cup Tournament Finals take center stage. Will Ospreay battles "Hangman" Adam Page in the Men's Tournament Final, with a coveted AEW World Championship match at All In on the line. On the women's side, the intensity is just as high: Mercedes Mon√© faces Jamie Hayter in the 2025 Women's Owen Hart Foundation Cup Final, and the winner will also earn a World Championship opportunity at All In. Plus many more.
